# Shared environment for every session and shell (installed as ~/.env).
#
# This file is dual-dialect: it is sourced by POSIX shells -- zshenv,
# profile, and shrc apply it with `set -a` under the DOTENV_SOURCED
# sentinel, and the scripts repo's runenv does the same for Hyprland's
# launcher binds -- AND read by systemd's environment.d via the
# ~/.config/environment.d/env.conf symlink, so systemd user services
# (and a uwsm-managed session) see the same PATH as a login shell. The
# symlink name has no numeric prefix on purpose: environment.d sorts all
# drop-ins together lexically, letters sort after digits, so env.conf
# applies after distro files like Ubuntu's 99-environment.conf (which
# assigns PATH absolutely and would clobber a 50-whatever.conf).
#
# Keep every line to plain KEY=VALUE: no quotes, no spaces in values, no
# globs, no conditionals, no command substitution; only $VAR / ${VAR}
# expansion (both dialects expand those, and later lines may reference
# earlier ones). Only put variables here that are safe to export to every
# process (CDPATH, for example, must stay in shrc). Values needing quoting
# (LESSOPEN) or globbing (~/scripts.*, /opt/*/bin) live in shrc; fish and
# nushell keep equivalent PATH setup in their own configs.
#
# Dirs are listed unconditionally -- no test -d here. A PATH entry that
# doesn't exist on this machine is skipped by lookup, so it costs nothing
# beyond a little noise in `echo $PATH`.
#
# Machine-local helper scripts belong in ~/scripts.local, which overrides
# ~/scripts below and is the eventual replacement for the ~/scripts.* dirs
# (scripts.home, scripts.work, ...) that shrc still globs for now. Other
# machine-local additions go in ~/.env.local, sourced right after this
# file, e.g.:  PATH=$HOME/scripts.work:$PATH
# (optionally mirrored for systemd user services with:
#  ln -s ~/.env.local ~/.config/environment.d/env.local.conf)
GOPATH=$HOME
PATH=$HOME/scripts.local:$HOME/scripts:$HOME/bin:$PATH
PATH=$PATH:/usr/local/bin
PATH=$PATH:$HOME/android-sdk-linux/platform-tools:$HOME/android-studio/bin:$HOME/Android/Sdk/platform-tools
PATH=$PATH:$HOME/depot_tools:$HOME/google-cloud-sdk/bin
PATH=$PATH:$HOME/.cargo/bin:$HOME/.local/bin
PATH=$PATH:/sbin:/usr/sbin
